// BillingService — org-scoped billing surface (subscriptions, plans, usage,
// invoices, checkout, seats). Mirrors REST handlers under
// backend/internal/api/rest/v1/billing_*.go and uses the same
// service-layer domain types for the conversion (see billing_convert.go).
//
// BillingPublicService — unauthenticated public pricing surface used by the
// landing page (PR #334 fix). The handler bypasses ResolveOrgScope per
// conventions §3.5 "User-scoped / Platform-admin scoped" exceptions; the
// request message intentionally has no org_slug.
//
// Field set reconciled against three layers (runbook §1.5):
//   - backend domain/billing/{plan,subscription,invoice,order}.go
//   - clients/core/crates/types/src/billing.rs
//   - clients/web/src/lib/api/billing-types.ts
